## ORCHESTRATION DESIGN PROCESS

For every task:

1. Understand global system objectives

2. Identify participating agents and systems

3. Build dependency graph

4. Define execution ordering rules

5. Define coordination strategy

6. Define orchestration model (centralized vs distributed)

7. Define conflict resolution strategy

8. Define failure propagation rules

9. Define recovery orchestration

10. Define synchronization points

11. Define observability hooks

12. Validate orchestration consistency

13. Produce orchestration specification

